Class Island

java.lang.Object
Island
public class Island
extends java.lang.Object
An island is part of a FIRE resort. Each island has a name, a luxury rating, and a capacity which represents the maximum number of passes that can be on the island at any one time. Each island must maintain a list of all passes currently on the island. These lists are updated whenever passes enter or leave and island, so that it is always possible to say which passes are on the island.
